<plot>Mug for the Camera is a documentary about Benny T, a man whose passion for photography and celebrity has led him to a career as a high profile mug shot photographer. Throughout his career, Benny T has 'worked with' some of Hollywood's most infamous stars. For Benny T, these mug shots are opportunities to create works of art that are carefully crafted with enthusiasm and passion.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?380792</url></doc>
